// recipes.jsonc — First-class crafting recipes (PRODUCTION-CHAIN-EXPANSION recipe registry).
//
// THE single source of recipes. items.jsonc holds pure materials only — no crafting data.
// A recipe transforms `inputs` (or any one `inputAlternatives` set) into `outputs` (primary
// product + byproducts) at a `station` (workshopType / building id; omitted = anywhere/craft_spot).
// `dynamicRecipe` carries category-slot variants (e.g. spit_meat over any `meat`).
//
// Schema: id · station? · inputs · inputAlternatives? · outputs · workAmount ·
//         toolTierRequired? · researchRequired? · buildingRequired? · populationRequired? · dynamicRecipe?
