  // BREW HERB TEA (campfire): herbs steeped in hot water → a calming `soothed` drink (the cooked outlet
  // for thyme/mint/sage). Eaten via the meal path like ale/wine, so its meal buff fires on consumption.
  {
    "id"              : "brew_herb_tea",
